00:17:01.330 --> 00:17:02.920
She can answer questions.

00:17:02.920 --> 00:17:03.580
She can paint.

00:17:03.580 --> 00:17:05.270
She can do all kinds of things.

00:17:05.270 --> 00:17:08.440
But she does not remember
