00:18:59.080 --> 00:18:59.980
OK?

00:18:59.980 --> 00:19:02.590
She cannot experience fear.

00:19:02.590 --> 00:19:05.290
She doesn't recognize
fear on facial expressions

00:19:05.290 --> 00:19:06.500
of other people.

