00:41:09.680 --> 00:41:11.770
OK, we're going
to-- oh, here we go.

00:41:11.770 --> 00:41:12.280
Oh, right.

00:41:12.280 --> 00:41:14.000
OK, just fixate on
the center again.

00:41:14.000 --> 00:41:14.500
Sorry.

00:41:14.500 --> 00:41:17.020
